summary: A performance FX, used to change the vibrancy of colors, and shading effects to produce an TES:IV like effect. For those who mildly dislike Skyrims color palate. And have a low-performance laptop like me.
descriptionHtml:
A performance FX, used to change the vibrance of colors, and shading effects to produce an TES:IV like effect. For those who mildly dislike skyrims colour pallate. And have a low-performance laptop like me. If you crash it's a problem with you not me. Runs on max setting on my i5 intel 4000 6gb ram at 50 fps so you have no excuses not to download other than personal taste. Hope you enjoy a throwbackish colors and shaders.

TO INSTALL YOU REQUIRE SWEETFX 1.5 
FROM HERE
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/23364/?

drag n drop and replace all files in your common/skyrim folder.
author: adrian85858
